#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kamoso; 3.2"
msgstr "&kamoso; 3.2"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "Take a shot"
msgstr "Posnemi fotografijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kamoso; gives you an opportunity to make photos from your webcam and upload "
"them to Internet"
msgstr ""
"&kamoso; vam omogoča, da s svojo spletno kamero naredite fotografije in jih "
"naložite na internet"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record video"
msgstr "Posnemi video"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kamoso; allows to record videos from your webcam and upload them to the "
"Internet"
msgstr ""
"&kamoso; omogoča snemanje videoposnetkov s spletne kamere in njihovo "
"nalaganje na internet"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Guide"
msgstr "Uporabniška navodila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Welcome to &kamoso;!"
msgstr "Dobrodošli v &kamoso;!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kamoso; is a great program to use your webcam to take pictures or make "
"videos. This guide will help you to use &kamoso; once you have installed it."
msgstr ""
"&kamoso; je odličen program za uporabo spletne kamere za fotografiranje ali "
"ustvarjanje videoposnetkov. Ta vodnik vam bo pomagal pri uporabi &kamoso; ko "
"ga namestite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Hitri začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On launching &kamoso;, it displays this window with buttons at the bottom:"
msgstr "Ko zažene &kamoso;, prikaže to okno z gumbi na dnu:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to <guibutton>Shoot</guibutton> mode to take one picture"
msgstr ""
"Preklopite v način <guibutton>Zajemi sliko</guibutton>, da posnamete eno "
"sliko"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to <guibutton>Burst</guibutton> mode and take continuously pictures "
"until you stop by clicking the middle button again"
msgstr ""
"Preklopite v način <guibutton>Zajemi slikovni rafal</guibutton> in "
"neprekinjeno fotografirajte, dokler se ne ustavite s ponovnim klikom na "
"srednji gumb"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to <guibutton>Record</guibutton> mode to record a video"
msgstr ""
"Preklopite v način <guibutton>Posnemi video</guibutton>, da posnamete video"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start or stop taking pictures or recording a video"
msgstr "Začnite ali ustavite fotografiranje ali snemanje videa"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show gallery"
msgstr "Prikaži galerijo"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show settings"
msgstr "Pokaži nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pictures and videos are numbered consecutively and saved automatically in "
"the <guilabel>Captures directory</guilabel> defined in the settings."
msgstr ""
"Slike in videi so zaporedno oštevilčeni in samodejno shranjeni v "
"<guilabel>imeniku posnetkov</guilabel>, ki je določen v nastavitvah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Captures"
msgstr "Upravljanje posnetkov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and manage your captured pictures or videos click the "
"<guibutton>Show gallery</guibutton> button. In the context menu for each "
"entry in the gallery you find actions to manage them:"
msgstr ""
"Za ogled in upravljanje zajetih slik ali videoposnetkov kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Prikaži galerijo</guibutton>. V kontekstnem meniju za vsak vnos v "
"galeriji najdete dejanja za njihovo upravljanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> to view your captures in the associated "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guimenuitem>Odpri</guimenuitem> za ogled vaših posnetkov v "
"povezani aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to delete pictures and videos open the captures folder in the "
"filemanager."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati slike in videoposnetke, odprite mapo posnetkov v "
"upravitelju datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next actions allow you to upload captures to the Internet or send them "
"to a contact or device."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja dejanja vam omogočajo, da posnetke naložite na internet ali jih "
"pošljete stiku ali napravi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guimenuitem>Save as</guimenuitem> to copy the complete content of the "
"gallery to a new folder."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guimenuitem>Shrani kot</guimenuitem> za kopiranje celotne vsebine "
"galerije v novo mapo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing"
msgstr "Prilagajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Show settings</guibutton> button to open the settings "
"panel. Click the button again to hide the settings panel."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Pokaži nastavitve</guibutton>, da odprete ploščo z "
"nastavitvami. Ponovno kliknite gumb, da skrijete ploščo z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to change the folder where &kamoso; saves pictures and videos, "
"change the <guilabel>Captures directory</guilabel> at the top."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti mapo, v kateri je &kamoso; shrani slike in "
"videoposnetke, spremenite <guilabel>imenik Captures</guilabel> na vrhu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable <guibutton>Use flash</guibutton> to highlight the window before "
"taking photos."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči <guibutton>Uporabi bliskavico</guibutton>, da označite okno pred "
"fotografiranjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the sliders you can modify camera settings like brightness, hue, "
"contrast, saturation and gamma."
msgstr ""
"Z drsniki lahko spreminjate nastavitve kamere, kot so svetlost, odtenek, "
"kontrast, nasičenost in gama."

